dct_title_s: The North Riding of York Shire
dct_description_sm: Dated from notes on Hodson p. 103 which say spelling Teises R. is 1695 edition. Shows boundaries, rivers, roads, woods, parks and settlements. Relief shown pictorially. London meridian. From Camden, William. Britannia, or a chorographical description of Great Britain and Ireland ... 1695. First state, produced prior to changes before 1722.
dct_publisher_sm: [London] : Sold by Abel Swale, Awnsham and Iohn Churchill, [1695]
dct_subject_sm: North Riding of Yorkshire (England)—Maps—Early works to 1800
dcat_theme_sm: North Riding of Yorkshire (England)—Maps—Early works to 1800
